  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "When the light client wants to retrieve some headers from the network, it needs the CHT to verify the response. \r\n\r\nBut the issue is if there is no CHT generated(chain height is less than 32768), light client has nothing to verify. Now it just refuses to send this kind of request.\r\n\r\nHow can we resolve this issue?",
